  "title": "Sales Executive (Food/ FMCG) - Car provided",
  "description": "<p>Our esteemed client in the <strong>Food</strong> <strong>Manufacturing industry</strong> is seeking a <strong>Sales Executive (F&amp;B) </strong>to join their dynamic team:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Employment Type: </strong>Permanent</li>\n  <li><strong>Position:</strong> Sales Executive</li>\n  <li><strong>Location:</strong> West, Singapore</li>\n  <li><strong>Working Hours:</strong> 5.5 days, Office Hours</li>\n  <li><strong>Salary Package:</strong> Up to $3,500 + Commission + AWS + Bonus (Company car, cashcard &amp; phone provided!)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Manage existing client accounts while developing new business opportunities.</li>\n  <li>Conduct field sales activities, including cold calling, networking, and client visits.</li>\n  <li>Build strong customer relationships and deliver excellent service.</li>\n  <li>Prepare sales forecasts, track performance, and provide regular reports.</li>\n  <li>Stay updated on market trends and customer needs to identify opportunities.</li>\n  <li>Ensure timely payment collection and maintain account discipline.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with team members and support the growth of assigned accounts.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>At least 2 years of related working experience.</li>\n  <li>Possess a valid Class 3 Driving License, company car will be provided.</li>\n  <li>Able to start immediately or in short notice.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Ready to apply? Here’s how:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Click the APPLY button, or</li>\n  <li>Email your resume (in MS Word or PDF format) to <a href=\"mailto:adelin@intuitrecruitment.com\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>adelin@intuitrecruitment.com</strong>.</a> Include the job title in your email subject line for prompt processing.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em><strong>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>By submitting your application, you consent to the collection and use of your personal data under Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Adelin Chong | EA Personnel Reg No.: R1875641</p>\n<p>Intuit Recruitment Pte Ltd | EA License No.: 25C2793</p>",
